---
/**
 * BlogArticleBody — Tier 2 blog composite (Story 4.4, AC7, AC9, AC11)
 *
 * Semantic <article> wrapper with Schema.org BlogPosting microdata.
 * Contains a <slot /> for the article header + prose content + future
 * integration points (related articles, inline CTA).
 *
 * Zero client-side JS — pure Astro component.
 */
---

<article
  itemscope
  itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting"
  class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
>
  <slot />
</article>
